{"id":232607119,"title":"給一位剛去實習的朋友","content":"有感而發\nhttps://i.imgur.com/hi5RTUb.jpg\n-\n各行各業都辛苦\n但”護理師”卻是不能比的\n他們肩上是扛著病患的生命\n還有每個家屬的期望\n壓力有多大\n想像一下你或許會明白\n-\n以前為了照顧家人\n整天待在醫院裡多達2個月\n放學就是跑去醫院\n徹夜沒睡看照家人\n早上再去學校補眠\n這段時間護理師們的辛勞、努力\n全看在眼裡\n有狀況時得第一時間出面處理\n要和很多不講理的家長溝通\n他們照顧我們的健康\n那他們的健康誰來照料\n多一點尊重 將心比心\n別再增加他們的壓力了\n-\n真的感謝所有醫護人員\n這絕對是個值得尊重的職業\n-\n辛苦你們了 加油(๑•̀ㅂ•́)و✧","excerpt":"有感而發，-，各行各業都辛苦，但”護理師”卻是不能比的，他們肩上是扛著病患的生命，還有每個家屬的期望，壓力有多大，想像一下你或許會明白，-，以前為了照顧家人，整天待在醫院裡多達2個月，放學就是跑去醫院","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"b22d2f5d-3c06-4d08-96b8-770eb38e8f96","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-01T14:54:04.972Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-01T15:02:26.386Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":59,"tags":[],"topics":["實習","護理","護理師"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"護理","forumAlias":"nursing","school":"南臺科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":58},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/hi5RTUb.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"da64a158-945b-4b88-a1f3-ffc95574cfbb","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hi5RTUbl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/hi5RTUbl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hi5RTUbl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-01T14:54:04.972Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-01T15:02:26.386Z"},{"id":"da64a158-945b-4b88-a1f3-ffc95574cfbb","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hi5RTUb.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/hi5RTUb","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hi5RTUbl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-01T14:54:04.972Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-01T15:02:26.386Z"}],"postAvatar":""}